<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.210724>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Nebulovena persa, female. Habitus. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/210724/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.210725>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Nebulovena persa. A) Head, anterior view; B) Female antenna; C) Male antenna, arrow indicating F 1 excavated; D) Mesosoma, lateral view; E) Mesosoma, dorsal view, arrows indicating circumscutellar carina; F) Radial cell; G) Metasoma, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/210725/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.210726>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Characters of Figitinae. A) Scutellum in dorsal view of Neralsia pseudoneralsia Jiménez & Pujade-Villar; B) scutellum in dorsal view of Xyalophoroides quinquelineata (Say); C) Scutellum in dorsal view of Neralsia acostullata Jiménez & Pujade-Villar; D) mesosoma in dorsal view of Xyalophora clavata (Giraud); E) mesosoma in dorsal view of Neralsia sp; F) scutellum in lateral view of Neralsia madrigalensis Jiménez & Pujade-Villar, arrow indicates interfoveal carina; G) head in frontal view of Xyalophora clavata; H) head in frontal view of Xyalophoroides quinquelineata; I) head in frontal view of Neralsia sp.; J) radial cell of X. quinquelineata; K) radial cell of Neralsia kiefferi Jiménez & Pujade-Villar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/210726/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.210727>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Characters of Figitinae + Melanips. A) Mesosoma, dorsal view, Lonchidia sp.; B) mesosoma, dorsal view, Paraschiza sp.; C) mesosoma, dorsal view, Melanips opacus (leg. Morphbank); D) Female antenna, Lonchidia sp. (leg. Morphbank); E) metasoma longer than head + mesosoma, Amphitectus sp.; F) head, anterior view, Melanips opacus (leg. Morphbank); G) radial cell, Melanips opacus (Hartig)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/210727/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

